{"tid":2409311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"與12名女子拍拖騙財2,500萬元 河南男被判無期徒刑","createTime":"2021-02-15T16:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T04:46:49.000Z","uid":346660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"134fc351cea72da31981fa72461b098ef3b12111","tid":2409311,"uid":346660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T16:51:30.000Z","msg":"河南男子楊某鋒以開順風車等名義故意接近女性，謊稱自己是大老闆並展開追求，再以資金周轉、拖欠工人工資等藉口騙財，兩年間共造成12名女子損失2,500萬元人民幣，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">其中包括兩名供職阿里巴巴的員工</span></span>。楊某鋒近日被法院判處無期徒刑。<br />\n另一名供職阿里巴巴的龐某，也被楊某鋒採取同樣手段，損失25萬元人民幣。杭州市人民檢察院指控，2017年下半年至2019年下半年期間，楊某鋒共騙取12名女性共計4,050餘萬元人民幣、125萬餘美元，歸還2,110餘萬元人民幣、22萬余元美元。調查發現，楊某鋒生活奢華，擁有一輛白色蘭博基尼SUV，還購買了蘋果電腦和多部手機。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55915e80858f492be0f315f2aab4a4fd3351825e","tid":2409311,"uid":346660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T16:52:07.000Z","msg":"初中屌打萬里挑一既阿里巴巴員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc216571d20fd10e67c468e19ea2eb5bd5608232","tid":2409311,"uid":36995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T17:10:53.000Z","msg":"事業有成/好Top既女人<br />\n特別鍾意幻想<br />\n美國海軍/投行CEO/科技股大老闆<br />\n然後一口氣呃晒老女人啲錢"},{"pid":"7449889eae04610fcac41a36e99e514246faa0b8","tid":2409311,"uid":229834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SgTydTU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSgTydTU.png&h=50afca51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gOhvf7f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgOhvf7f.png&h=e32a2fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LE9xusg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLE9xusg.png&h=2dcc5fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2500萬夠食幾多餐豬扒同買幾多部macbook pro"